Package: ggbasketball
Type: Package
Title: `ggplot2` Based Visualization of Basketball Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Yishu", "Xue", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "xueyishu2436@gmail.com"))
Description: Analytics of sports data depends a lot on visualizations. For
  basketball data, creating visualizaitons is often time consuming. This package
  aims to simplify the process by providing easy-to-use functions for creating
  visualizations for basketball data.
